high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the couch.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the couch.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then turn left to face the chair with the pillow on it.
Put the blue credit card on the front edge of the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move a blue credit card to the seat of a chair.

high_descs: Make a left and then a right to reach the longer brown couch.
Pick up the credit card from the brown couch.
Turn right to reach the smaller brown armchair.
Set the credit card down on the smaller brown armchair.
anns.task_desc: Move a credit card from the longer brown couch to the smaller brown armchair.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the couch, facing the middle of it.
Pick up the credit card on the couch.
Turn right and walk to the chair next to the couch.
Place the credit card on the chair, in front of the left side of the pillow.
anns.task_desc: Place a credit card on a chair.
